  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'No one can be born more than once.


      That means you''ll be
      stuck here forever unless we can find a solution!

'
    nextOption: Uh Oh
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Go up the stairs behind me and commune with the fountain of time.


      Maybe
      it can see how you ended up back here.'
    nextOption: You have a talking fountain?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'It''s more like a focus for time streams that allows you to look
      through a quantum reality splicer and...


      Oh, I can see you eyes glazing
      over already.


      Fine then.  Yes, we have a talking fountain...'
    nextOption: Neat, I'll go see it now
